---
import ProblemCard from "./problemCard.astro";
---

<section id="problem" class="py-16 lg:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">

    <div
            class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none aria-hidden"
            aria-hidden="true"
    >
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(59,130,246,0.03)_0%,transparent_70%)]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 box-border">

        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 md:mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6 font-display font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white">
                El <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent inline-block">Problema</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-pretty font-medium">
                Las estafas digitales son cada vez más sofisticadas. Identificar una amenaza a tiempo es el mayor desafío en el entorno digital actual.
            </p>
        </div>

        <ProblemCard />

    </div>
</section>